## **Examples**

- **Satellite frontend (mosc-temp): commit feature + deploy via release:**
  ```powershell
  cd F:\project_workspace\mosc-temp
  git add -A
  git diff --cached --name-only | Select-String 'prod\.env|auth\.json'
  git commit -m "feat(mosc-redesign): downloads migration and SQL refresh"
  git checkout release/v1.0.0
  git reset --hard MOSC-redesign-sub-poc-2
  $env:GIT_SSL_NO_VERIFY = "true"
  git push origin release/v1.0.0
  Remove-Item Env:GIT_SSL_NO_VERIFY
  ```

- **Test-site (already on release):**
  ```powershell
  cd F:\project_workspace\event-site-front-end-test-site
  git add -A
  git diff --cached --name-only | Select-String 'prod\.env|auth\.json'
  git commit -m "feat(mosc-redesign): sync with mosc-temp baseline"
  $env:GIT_SSL_NO_VERIFY = "true"
  git push origin release/v1.0.0
  Remove-Item Env:GIT_SSL_NO_VERIFY
  ```

- **Template (main only):**
  ```powershell
  cd F:\project_workspace\event-site-front-end-template
  git add -A
  git commit -m "feat: sync cursor rules and migration tooling"
  git push origin main
  ```

